{"tid":1863893,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有預感觀塘區將會係好嚴重嘅疫區","createTime":"2020-02-05T10:41:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-05T11:11:44.000Z","uid":346057,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"90c766d1d8758d042161534e5488eedf2494756d","tid":1863893,"uid":346057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:41:53.000Z","msg":"小弟第一次開po<br />\n作為藍到發黑嘅藍塘<br />\n廢老多 新移民多 舊大廈多 屋邨多<br />\n班仆街廢老又唔衛生<br />\n又吐痰又喂雀又大大力咳<br />\n就算佢地肯戴口罩都除低食煙<br />\n咁唔衛生 好難唔爆發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以上都唔算重點 應該好多區都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重點係<br />\n首先啟德郵輪碼頭嘅交通主要係來往九龍灣/觀塘/藍田<br />\n落船冇病唔代表你真係冇中招<br />\n屌你老母一落船就過黎東九龍傳播病菌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n第二 如心艾朗酒店<br />\n其實間酒店好近黨鐵站同民居<br />\n問都冇問過就攞黎做隔離？<br />\n仲要記得之前黎咗一兩團武漢人<br />\n唔知係咪同一間酒店(呢個好似冇乜人講)<br />\n仲有 當大家關注緊美孚同西貢嘅時候<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">點解冇乜人提九龍灣健康中心架<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n政府先斬後奏徵用咗黎做指定診所<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n近民居之餘<br />\n出入都要經九龍東嘅交通<br />\n九龍東人自求多福了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有病徵記得去搵警察叔叔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d14e6be35567da90fec1538f1fec2725ccf73511","tid":1863893,"uid":346057,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T10:46:27.000Z","msg":"仆街 我好似開錯台"},{"pid":"0ce33679f4111ff77fafe2529106f2700f3014db","tid":1863893,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:05:34.000Z","msg":"所以nben 係Punisher <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/agree2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0549ea92700035329215ed8e68619bd8049425d4","tid":1863893,"uid":106290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:07:56.000Z","msg":"啲人成日都話要攬炒 <br />\n宜家啲人有病唔去睇醫生 <br />\n就係想成個香港都攬炒 <br />\n如果有10萬人都中 唔知會點呢"},{"pid":"10cf2c229fc216f49e9b09ec5ce3d8fc2a62aa6e","tid":1863893,"uid":313630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-05T11:11:44.000Z","msg":"話會社區爆發個陣開始<br />\n已經覺得觀塘好危<br />\n<br />\n住觀塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}